---
title: Bacon & Basil Pesto Potato Salad with Parmesan & Almonds | Serves 2
description: We are stepping it up with this spin on the classic potato salad with crispy bacon, basil pesto and juicy tomatoes.
Ready in 15 minutes, this quick lunch is packed with flavour and can be prepped the day before or made on the spot!
